1
00:00:14,682 --> 00:00:20,146
Connecting old words
that have been used up

2
00:00:20,938 --> 00:00:24,567
I just want to convey

3
00:00:25,317 --> 00:00:28,904
my simple thoughts

4
00:00:28,988 --> 00:00:34,118
That day's faint wind blows away

5
00:00:35,119 --> 00:00:38,414
at the castle ruins of yesterday

6
00:00:39,498 --> 00:00:44,587
I'll laugh with you
and live for the moment

7
00:00:45,337 --> 00:00:52,219
Still that incident
will continue to trouble you, right?

8
00:00:53,554 --> 00:00:57,057
That's why it must be good-bye

9
00:00:57,141 --> 00:01:00,603
Leaving nothing behind,

10
00:01:00,686 --> 00:01:04,231
let us share what is left

11
00:01:04,315 --> 00:01:11,280
In time, we'll realize
that it was everything

12
00:01:11,363 --> 00:01:14,742
And sadness will touch our cheeks,

13
00:01:14,825 --> 00:01:18,454
creating a river of tears

14
00:01:18,537 --> 00:01:24,293
Trembling thoughts swept into a vortex

15
00:01:24,376 --> 00:01:28,881
and melting away

16
00:01:39,058 --> 00:01:41,143
Where's the other one?

17
00:01:41,227 --> 00:01:42,228
Hey...

18
00:01:44,271 --> 00:01:45,898
Who are you looking for?

19
00:01:48,359 --> 00:01:52,655
I'll take care of the rest.
Go wash your eyes in that river.

20
00:01:56,659 --> 00:02:00,913
This is my ability...
specializing in assassination, of course.

21
00:02:00,996 --> 00:02:05,626
You can't beat me by just having
a good nose and nails...

22
00:02:06,293 --> 00:02:08,671
You can't beat my ability!

23
00:02:18,514 --> 00:02:21,934
Akamaru... I'm sorry...

24
00:02:22,017 --> 00:02:25,771
Akamaru...
We've always done things together.

25
00:02:25,855 --> 00:02:27,982
We were together
whenever and wherever.

26
00:02:28,774 --> 00:02:32,570
However this one time, I'm sunk.

27
00:02:33,070 --> 00:02:37,908
My cells can swim inside
your body as I wish,

28
00:02:37,992 --> 00:02:40,536
and I can even create parts
that are only you.

29
00:02:40,619 --> 00:02:43,622
In other words,
a little bit of a fusion condition...

30
00:02:43,706 --> 00:02:46,041
a sharing of the flesh is what it'll be.

31
00:02:47,376 --> 00:02:49,628
A sharing...?

32
00:02:49,712 --> 00:02:51,046
That's right!

33
00:02:51,130 --> 00:02:54,633
And a cruel way of killing
that only I can accomplish...

34
00:02:55,217 --> 00:02:59,138
the gradual scraping off
of just your cells!

35
00:02:59,722 --> 00:03:01,015
I see...

36
00:03:08,522 --> 00:03:10,149
If that's the case...!

37
00:03:19,241 --> 00:03:23,037
If I do this...
what's gonna happen?

38
00:03:24,914 --> 00:03:28,292
Suicide?! That's ridiculous!

39
00:03:30,544 --> 00:03:32,296
Die with me...

40
00:03:35,299 --> 00:03:36,967
To Each His Own Battle

41
00:04:03,827 --> 00:04:06,830
What are you thinking?!

42
00:04:15,089 --> 00:04:21,178
It's just as I thought...
We are sharing one body, right?

43
00:04:21,261 --> 00:04:22,471
Damn it!

44
00:04:23,347 --> 00:04:27,768
Entering my opponent's body
to avoid any attacks...

45
00:04:27,851 --> 00:04:30,604
that is my Jutsu's greatest advantage.

46
00:04:31,522 --> 00:04:33,273
There hasn't been
a single one before now

47
00:04:33,357 --> 00:04:34,858
