48
00:04:36,318 --> 00:04:37,611
Are you in pain?

49
00:04:38,112 --> 00:04:41,365
All right then, let's get comfortable now.

50
00:04:43,325 --> 00:04:46,078
Yikes, you idiot!
Stop it!

51
00:04:46,161 --> 00:04:47,538
