and fled.

57
00:05:53,312 --> 00:05:57,983
It's the right decision,
but he's more cold-hearted than me.

58
00:06:09,745 --> 00:06:11,747
What?!
It couldn't be!

59
00:06:32,810 --> 00:06:36,355
What a relief...
He's still breathing.

60
00:06:40,567 --> 00:06:41,860
What a relief!

61
00:06:57,417 --> 00:07:01,130
Akamaru... You really gave it your best.

62
00:07:02,131 --> 00:07:05,467
Because of you, I was able to hold up
the enemy for a while.

63
00:07:05,968 --> 00:07:07,761
