69
00:08:01,106 --> 00:08:04,526
I'm Kiba. Nice to meet you, Akamaru.

70
00:08:13,202 --> 00:08:15,162
You!

71
00:08:28,258 --> 00:08:30,052
We've been together forever.

72
00:08:34,056 --> 00:08:35,891
Nice catch, Akamaru!

73
00:08:38,352 --> 00:08:41,021
All right, you did well!

74
00:08:42,189 --> 00:08:43,232
Here we go!

75
00:08:52,074 --> 00:08:53,784
Be more serious about it!

76
00:08:57,079 --> 00:08:59,331
Stop being such a baby!

77
00:08:59,414 --> 00:09:00,499
Mom...

78
00:09:08,757 --> 00:09:09,758
Listen, Kiba...

79
00:09:10,550 --> 00:09:11,927
It's not just you.

80
00:09:12,010 --> 00:09:13,428
Akamaru and you,

81
00:09:13,512 --> 00:09:15,389
the two of you need
to become strong together.

82
00:09:16,640 --> 00:09:19,893
With Akamaru... Together?

83
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:24,690
Akamaru...

84
00:09:35,117 --> 00:09:36,326
That's right.

85
00:09:40,789 --> 00:09:43,292
Way to go Akamaru! You did it!

86
00:09:43,375 --> 00:09:45,877
Mid-air Dynamic Marking!

87
00:09:46,837 --> 00:09:50,340
Next is mid-air triple somersault!
Take your aim!

88
00:09:57,681 --> 00:09:59,016
Yahoo!

89
00:10:03,687 --> 00:10:05,314
Yahoo!

90
00:10:20,370 --> 00:10:22,706
We'll be together forever
from now on too...

91
00:10:23,749 --> 00:10:26,918
I'll protect you from now on!

92
00:10:34,426 --> 00:10:35,761
That jerk!

93
00:10:36,636 --> 00:10:39,348
