Sakon!

97
00:11:13,590 --> 00:11:14,841
Sakon!

98
00:11:18,387 --> 00:11:21,139
Blah blah blah.
You're such a nuisance, Big Brother.

99
00:11:21,223 --> 00:11:23,934
Your yelling stings my eyes...

100
00:11:25,602 --> 00:11:26,728
Big Brother!

101
00:11:26,812 --> 00:11:29,106
I'll kill him... is what I'd like to do,

102
00:11:29,189 --> 00:11:31,149
but it's almost time for my sleep.

103
00:11:31,733 --> 00:11:34,903
Capture those bastards alive in my place.

104
00:11:35,904 --> 00:11:38,240
When I wake up,
I'll kill them.

105
00:11:38,323 --> 00:11:41,326
All right, Sakon?
Capture them alive...

106
00:11:41,827 --> 00:11:44,871
Yeah, I got it...
But...

107
00:11:46,081 --> 00:11:48,208
The killing part,
we'll do it together.

108
00:12:19,531 --> 00:12:21,199
If I carelessly attack,

109
00:12:21,283 --> 00:12:23,535
