and I end up attacking myself!

110
00:12:54,858 --> 00:12:55,984
Behold!

111
00:12:56,067 --> 00:12:57,152
Willow Dance!

112
00:13:23,220 --> 00:13:24,346
You!

113
00:13:42,405 --> 00:13:43,740
Bones?

114
00:13:53,500 --> 00:13:56,836
This is my...Kekkei Genkai.

115
00:14:24,698 --> 00:14:26,825
What's with this guy...?

116
00:14:27,534 --> 00:14:30,495
Is he attacking with bones sticking out
from all over his body?

117
