137
00:17:12,907 --> 00:17:17,579
Damn, I did save Akamaru
for the time being,

138
00:17:17,662 --> 00:17:19,748
but maybe I went too far.

139
00:17:40,226 --> 00:17:43,271
This smell...
What does it mean?

140
00:17:44,981 --> 00:17:48,943
Why... Why is it that even those guys
are headed to a place like this?!

141
00:17:49,444 --> 00:17:51,738
