150
00:19:00,598 --> 00:19:01,975
Damn!

151
00:19:07,647 --> 00:19:08,898
Damn!

152
00:19:16,823 --> 00:19:17,949
Damn...

153
00:19:18,825 --> 00:19:20,034
This is it!

154
00:19:20,910 --> 00:19:24,789
So, I've cornered you, you stinking rat!

155
00:19:28,376 --> 00:19:30,003
Pretty impressive...

156
