understand this song.

164
00:19:58,907 --> 00:20:04,329
You're so right...
since art is so foreign to me.

165
00:20:05,371 --> 00:20:09,000
But since she uses that flute
to manipulate,

166
00:20:09,083 --> 00:20:13,171
